She didn't wait for Megatron to reply. She was hurting and wanted repairs 
done.  She stepped intot he CR chamber and closed the door.

After a while, she walked out of the chamber fuuly repaired.  She walked 
over to Megatron in wolf mode.  She looked at him.

"Sorry , but I needed that.  Now then, If you are in need of another 
fighter, I'd like to join your party.  If not, then I'll take my leave now 
and not bother you again."
